How to buy

Create a Wallet

Download a software wallet that is compatible with PulseChain such as InternetMoney.io, Rabby, or MetaMask. You can also tie this to your favorite hardware wallet for extra security!

Get Some PLS

If you do not already have some PLS on PulseChain you can use a service such as ChangeNOW.io to swap from ETH or other native L1 tokens to PLS on PulseChain.

Go to 9inch Exchange

Go to app.9inch.io and use the link to access the exchange. Connect your wallet and confirm you can see your PLS in your wallet. Next take the contract address adove and add $TEVE to your token list.

Swap PLS for $TEVE

Swap PLS for $TEVE. $TEVE has ZERO taxes so you don’t need to worry about buying with a specific slippage, although you may need to use slippage during times of market volatility.
